metadata.name: January Revolution
metadata.description:
January Revolution of every bissextile February, which took place on Tuesday according to the Google calendar, but 1337 days and 23 hrs ago according to the Etherscan calendar. Many minds gathered, great ideas were born, but nothing happened*. Nobody moved. Nobody threw a stone. Some fell down**. Commoners watched the scene but were very careful not to participate in it. It was awesome!

*Mlibty Shadows have no ears, so can't hear one another
**Mlibty Shadows have no legs and arms, they fall easily. Others can't help them to stand up again, because they have no legs, no arms and no ears.
